title: Redmi Note 9
description: The Redmi Note 9 is available in three variants; 4GB of RAM with 64GB of storage, 4GB of RAM with 128GB of storage, and 6GB of RAM with 128GB of storage.

title: Canon 90D Dslr Camera
description: The 90D is essentially the DSLR version of the mirrorless EOS M6 Mark II, which was introduced alongside it.The Canon EOS 90D camera features a powerful 32.5 Megapixel CMOS (APS-C) sensor that can capture high-resolution images.

title: Mac Air Apple Laptop
description: Apple MacBook Air MQD32HN/A is a macOS laptop with a 13.30-inch display that has a resolution of 1440x900 pixels. It is powered by a Core i5 processor and it comes with 8GB of RAM.
